  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA298-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">itu tōḻiyāl poruḷ valippittut talaimakaḷai eyti āṟṟatāya neñciṉai (ET: neñciṟku) neruṅkic collit talaimakaṉ celavu aḻuṅkiyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is how HE dispenses with going, speaking towards [his own] heart that was unable to bear it when reaching HER wo was forced [to favour] wealth by the confidante.</p>
        </div>
      <div xml:id="NA298">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            vampa mākkaḷ varutiṟa nōkkic</l>
<l>            ceṅkaṇai toṭutta ceyirnōk kāṭavar</l>
<l>            maṭivāyt taṇṇumait taḻaṅkukural kēṭṭa</l>
<l>            veruvaic cēval kiḷaivayiṟ peyaru</l>
<l>            maruñcurak kavalai yañcuvaru naṉantalaip </l>
<l>            perumpal kuṉṟa muḷḷiyu maṟṟivaḷ</l>
<l>            karumpuṭaip paṇaittō ṇōkkiyu morutiṟam</l>
<l>            paṟṟāy vāḻiye ṉeñcē naṟṟārp</l>
<l>            poṟṟērc ceḻiyaṉ kūṭa lāṅka</l>
<l>            ṇorumai ceppiya varumai vāṉmukai </l>
<l>            yirumpōtu kamaḻuṅ kūntal</l>
<l>            perumalai taḻīiyunōk kiyaiyumō maṟṟē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Whether you remember the great many hills</l>
<l rend="indent2">in the vast area, where fear comes up on the crossroads</l>
<l rend="indent">of the difficult desert,</l>
<l rend="indent">when the male kite moves over to [its] relations,</l>
<l rend="indent">hearing the resounding voice of the Taṇṇumai drum with upturned mouth</l>
<l rend="indent3">of men with angry looks who have linked [their] straight arrows,</l>
<l rend="indent3">looking to the side where new people would come,</l>
<l>or whether you look just at her bamboo shoulder with sugar-cane [drawing],</l>
<l>you won’t cling to one side, oh my heart.</l>
<l>Even when adopting<note place="foot">Here the choice of <term xml:lang="ta">taḻuvu</term> is not accidental: embracing the mountains instead of HER.</note> the big mountains,</l>
<l rend="indent4">will it really be enjoyable to look</l>
<l rend="indent2">at [her] tresses that are fragrant with dark buds</l>
<l rend="indent2">[and] bright buds of a rareness that speaks of the unity(?)<note place="ta">How to understand <term xml:lang="ta">orumai ceppiya arumai</term>?</note></l>
<l rend="indent3">there in Kūṭal of Ceḻiyaṉ with golden chariot [and] good garland?</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
